				<Title>
					<Text>Minecart Depot</Text>
				</Title>
				<Icon>
					<Name>Minecart Depot</Name>
					<Alignment>Center</Alignment>
				</Icon>
				<Paragraph>
					<Text>Minecart Depots are the method used to place Minecarts onto your minecart network. Simply place a Storage Hopper adjacent to the Depot, and ensure the Depot is touching any piece of track. Each Depot is limited to a single Minecart placement per 30 seconds, to give time for the internals to cool down.</Text>
				</Paragraph>
				<Spacer/>
				<Spacer/>
				<Paragraph>
					<Text>Minecart usage is straightforwards, and simply expands on the Hopper -&gt; Conveyor paradigm that has been used until now. Minecarts are loaded onto your minecart network via a Minecart Depot.</Text>
&gt;
				</Paragraph>
